sequenceDiagram
    actor Teacher
    participant Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant HRAT as HRAT Engine (in-memory)
    participant ML as ML Model (joblib)
    participant SHAP as SHAP Explainer
    participant DB as Database

    Teacher->>Frontend: Select student, start screening
    Frontend->>API: POST /screenings/session/start {student_id}
    API->>DB: Verify student exists & belongs to teacher
    DB-->>API: Student confirmed
    API->>HRAT: create_session(student_id, student_name)
    HRAT-->>API: session_id + Q1 (Phase 1: Gateway)
    API-->>Frontend: {session_id, question, progress 1/20}
    Frontend-->>Teacher: Display Q1

    loop Phase 1 — 5 Gateway Questions (one per LD domain)
        Teacher->>Frontend: Submit answer (score 1–5)
        Frontend->>API: POST /session/answer {session_id, question_id, score}
        API->>HRAT: record answer, update domain suspicion scores
        HRAT-->>API: next question + progress
        API-->>Frontend: {question, progress n/20}
        Frontend-->>Teacher: Display next question
    end

    note over HRAT: Phase 2 routing: rank domains by suspicion<br/>Rank 1&2 → 4 deep-dive questions each<br/>Rank 3 → 2 questions, Rank 4&5 → 1 each

    loop Phase 2 — 12 Domain-Prioritised Questions
        Teacher->>Frontend: Submit answer (score 1–5)
        Frontend->>API: POST /session/answer {session_id, question_id, score}
        API->>HRAT: record answer, route by priority
        HRAT-->>API: next question + progress
        API-->>Frontend: {question, progress n/20}
        Frontend-->>Teacher: Display next question
    end

    loop Phase 3 — 3 Fill Questions (highest-suspicion gaps)
        Teacher->>Frontend: Submit answer (score 1–5)
        Frontend->>API: POST /session/answer {session_id, question_id, score}
        API->>HRAT: record final answers
        HRAT-->>API: next question or null (if complete)
        API-->>Frontend: {question or null, progress 20/20}
    end

    Teacher->>Frontend: Complete screening + submit observation notes
    Frontend->>API: POST /screenings/session/complete {session_id, student_id, nlp_notes}
    API->>HRAT: finalize(session_id)
    HRAT-->>API: {feature_vector [20 scores], routing_summary}

    API->>ML: predict_with_explanation(feature_vector)
    ML->>SHAP: compute SHAP values per LD
    SHAP-->>ML: top contributing features per LD
    ML-->>API: {ld_scores[5], shap_values, narrative}

    API->>DB: Save Screening(answers, nlp_notes)
    API->>DB: Save PredictionResult(ld_scores)
    HRAT->>HRAT: delete_session(session_id)

    API-->>Frontend: {screening_id, predictions, explanations, narrative}
    Frontend-->>Teacher: Display screening results & SHAP narrative
